{"tid":1441714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公民教育] 文宣新方向","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:36:27.000Z","uid":140353,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd8c49403c85105d5c03548170478eb6bdf3547","tid":1441714,"uid":140353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:24:27.000Z","msg":"第一次開po 有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想 喺街派傳單 藍絲中立派老人家可能會無興趣/唔想拎 喺街拎咗翻到去又未必仔細睇<br />\n<br />\n道歉行動對形象好好 好多中年人討論 但難免有煩膠藍絲搞事 <br />\n<br />\n如果整啲小冊子 <strong>圖文並茂咁解釋五大訴求</strong>警黑勾結濫權 選擇性執法 具體咁用數字 (用咗幾多tg 拉咗幾多白衣人 vs 殺龍巴絲 etc.) 用圖 (721元朗 vs 728速龍衝元朗站) 用字解釋吓 (越精簡越好) 再<strong>同場加映道歉啟示 </strong>  然後派/寄去信箱 有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過小冊子始終無咁update 如果可以放埋QR code 連去一個website keep住update 每日發生嘅野 / youtube channel 就perfect <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為收信中年人唔會唔睇 兼且可以接觸好大嘅年齡層 寄到過去佢地可以慢慢研究 俾佢地感覺我地有心 而且叫做迫佢地接收吓cctvb外嘅資訊 錢方面可以眾籌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw, 五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae15306389af71efe4993ce6d372311b5f160bff","tid":1441714,"uid":140353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f5def2e42737a640fa14977e6193faeea8397e2","tid":1441714,"uid":140353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897d583971e8c7766c1fe7426ad283256f2853ac","tid":1441714,"uid":140353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121cc7122d888601068956bea6869e6dc33ad610","tid":1441714,"uid":140353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /